<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>今天吃什么</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="./style.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <main class="app">
    <section class="hero">
      <p class="eyebrow">Meal Randomizer</p>
      <h1>今天吃什么？</h1>
      <p class="desc">早餐随机 1 个，午餐/晚餐自动生成“一荤一素”。直接点击转盘中心开抽，停稳后结果一个一个跳出来。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel question-panel">
      <h2 id="questionText">今晚吃什么？</h2>
      <div class="meal-tabs" role="group" aria-label="选择用餐场景">
        <button class="meal-btn" data-meal="breakfast">早餐</button>
        <button class="meal-btn" data-meal="lunch">午餐</button>
        <button class="meal-btn active" data-meal="dinner">晚餐</button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="wheel-section">
      <div class="wheel-card">
        <div class="pointer"></div>
        <div class="wheel" id="wheel"></div>
        <div class="wheel-hint">点击转盘中心「开抽」，多圈会同时反向旋转 3 秒</div>
      </div>

      <div class="result-card panel">
        <p class="result-label">本次推荐</p>
        <div id="resultBox" class="result-box empty">
          直接点击左侧转盘中心，开始决定今天吃什么。
        </div>
        <div class="interaction-note">不再单独放按钮，转盘本身就是主要交互入口。</div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="panel history-panel">
      <div class="section-title-row">
        <h3>最近 7 天记录</h3>
        <button id="clearHistoryBtn" class="text-btn">清空记录</button>
      </div>
      <div id="historyList" class="history-list"></div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script src="./app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
